OL,3,CFormer surveyor awarded #145k after
OL,4,Ccollapse of building firm
OL,6,FA former surveyor has been awarded
OL,7,F#145k in compensation for being
OL,8,Funfairly dismissed when the Jersey
OL,9,Fbuilding company he worked for
OL,10,Fcollapsed.
OL,12,FStephen Romeril had worked for AC
OL,13,FMauger & Son Limited for 49 years
OL,14,Fbefore his employment was terminated
OL,15,Fon 14 August 2025, after Style Group,
OL,16,Fof which the company was part,
OL,17,Fsuddenly collapsed.
