OL,3,CFormer surveyor awarded #145k after
OL,4,Ccollapse of building firm
OL,6,FMr Romeril argued at an Employment and
OL,7,FDiscrimination Tribunal that he had
OL,8,Flost his job without the right
OL,9,Fprocesses or notice.
OL,11,FHe said he had not only been unfairly
OL,12,Fdismissed but was entitled to notice
OL,13,Fpay, holiday pay and unpaid wages.
OL,15,FHe also sought damages for breaches of
OL,16,Fhis contractual rights.
OL,18,FThe liquidators of AC Mauger decided
OL,19,Fnot to defend the proceedings.
