OL,3,CFormer surveyor awarded #145k after
OL,4,Ccollapse of building firm
OL,6,FAdvocate Dr Elena Moran, who was
OL,7,Foverseeing the tribunal, decided he
OL,8,Fwas entitled to #87,819 for unfair
OL,9,Fdismissal, #23,418 for notice pay and
OL,10,F#3,903 for holiday pay.
OL,12,FMr Romeril has also been awarded
OL,13,F#30,000 for breach of his contractual
OL,14,Frights.
OL,16,FIn total, he was awarded #145,141 in
OL,17,Fcompensation.
